name: Stand On Principle
description:
The last edition of the collection of my favorite photos using a cellphone,
this place is very difficult to get to, a road trip that takes 3 hours by motorbike and 2 hours on foot, but because I was determined to be able to arrive and take photos of this amazing place, even though I often wanted to give up but finally I arrived and was able to enjoy the splendor of the water this plunge.
